      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, bot. Garden, ¶ 21/1/66. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to sanction the following expenditure in this establishment to meet the first current liabilities of...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.01.21a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">N66/895, unit 177, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, bot. Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">21/1/66.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to sanction the following expenditure in this establishment to meet the first current liabilities of the year.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Salary of the Gov. Botanist and Director for the month of January 1866</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£50.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>16/8d</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Salary of the Assistant</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£25.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Wages for the month of January</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£400.- .-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reference to this latter item I may remark, that it exceeds somewhat the estimated average sum of the wages fund for one month; the excess of expenditure was however unavoidable to keep the vast number of trees planted in the garden &amp; reserve alive during the distressing period of drought, though all the Garden employees have had over and over extra night-duties, for which no extrapayment will be rendered.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Approval for<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's request was initialled on the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>file.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient &amp; humble servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable the Chief Secretary.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
